    <%= image_tag 'milesImages/img_2.png', alt: 'Miles with brothers, wife, and dogs', class: 'feature-image small-image' %>
    <p> Beyond my academic and professional pursuits, I am deeply rooted in family values. I recently celebrated my
      marriage in October and cherish the time spent with my two brothers, wife, and dogs. My interests extend beyond the
      realm of technology, as I find joy in travel, gaming, anime, outdoor activities, and maintaining an active lifestyle.

    <p> In summary, I am an aspiring electrical engineer with a robust academic background, a passion for sustainability,
